'''''Gurmat Parkash''''' is a monthly [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]] magazine published by Dharam Prachar Committee of [[Shiromani Gurdwara Parbandhak Committee]],<ref>{{cite news|title=SGPC to identify routes taken by Guru Gobind Singh, Banda Singh Bahadur|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/chandigarh/sgpc-to-identify-routes-taken-by-guru-gobind-singh-banda-singh-bahadur/|accessdate=16 October 2016|work=The Indian Express|date=3 March 2016}}</ref> [[Amritsar]]. Its [[Hindi]] version is popularly known as ''Gurmat Gyan''.<ref>[http://www.sgpc.net/gurmat_parkash/index_main.asp Gurmat Parkash Magazine Official Page]</ref> This magazine covers various researched articles by different scholars on philosophical, historical and theological aspect of [[Sikh]] Religion. It also covers research articles on Sikh personalities, Events and present situations of Sikhs and Sikhism around the world.
